dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines. Cover title: The "Royal gazette" map of Bermuda. Inset map: Diagram of part of the Atlantic Ocean on Mercator's projection. Includes: Diagram showing the prevailing winds at Bermuda in each quarter of the year. From the Admiralty Pilot Charts of the North Atlantic Ocean, 1868. Originally folded in covers 16 x 9 cm.
dct_publisher_sm: Hamilton, Bermuda : Published by Lee & Co, [1868?]
